About Cold Lovers

Some stories don't have happy endings. Some loves leave scars instead of memories. This is a space for those storiesthe ones that ache, the ones that linger, the ones we carry like stones in our pockets.

Cold Lovers is a collection of short fiction exploring the darker corridors of the heart. These are tales of missed connections, quiet goodbyes, and the ghosts we make of the living.

Every story here is fiction, but every emotion is real. Because sometimes the only way to understand our own heartbreak is to read someone else's.

New stories released monthly. Subscribe to carry these words with you.

Written in the spaces between.
